Description-Content-Type: text/markdown

mcp-cloud-ops MCP server exposing read-only cloud CLI helpers.

Tools:
- aws
- kubectl
- helm
- search_context

Requires CLIs in PATH.

Run:
```bash
python -m src.cloud_ops.server
```
